posts.postTitle: Improved styling and added new methods
posts.postContent: Hurried day today! I was able to find some time later in the day and take a look at that navbar that was bothering me. Lots of progress there! Also, I’ve added some new links in the homepage. Will take a better look at it tomorrow.
